# ⚡ Substation AI - Environment Configuration Template
# Copy this file to '.env' in the same folder.
# NOTE: Since this is a serverless client-side HTML application running on the 'file:///' protocol,
# browser security rules (CORS) prevent fetching local filesystem files directly.
# The most secure and recommended way is to enter the key in the settings panel of the web application.

GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE
